=== MEMBERS ===

**Theo 'Ghost' Ramos** — *The True Believer*
- Brujah, 11th gen, Anarch, Sol-trained but Sol-disillusioned
- Embraced 2008, apparent age 24, he/him
- Public role: Pilsen Anarch foot soldier; sometimes cited by 
  Sol as 'a younger generation that needs more time to develop'
- Personal: Mexican-American, born in Pilsen, slight build, 
  shaved head, multiple tattoos including the Anarch ankh-fist 
  on his throat; carries a Glock 19 and a tactical knife
- Tells: Speaks in Spanish-English code-switching at high frequency; 
  always wears black; touches the throat tattoo when angry
- Code: Will not harm Pilsen mortals; will not betray Anarch 
  Council to outsiders; will absolutely betray Sol to a more 
  radical Anarch faction if the opportunity arises
- Internal contradiction: Idolized Sol when she Embraced him into 
  the Movement AND now considers her a traitor to the cause AND 
  cannot reconcile these two emotional truths

**Maya Brennan** — *The Strategist*
- Caitiff, 12th gen, Anarch, the coterie's planning mind
- Embraced 2016, apparent age 32, she/they
- Public role: One of Sol's recognized Pilsen lieutenants 
  (fourth-tier, but recognized); operates a small bar on Cermak 
  that doubles as Anarch meeting space
- Personal: Irish-American, mid-length brown hair, dark eyes, 
  perpetually in jeans and band t-shirts under a denim jacket; 
  the only member of the coterie Sol has actually trusted with 
  responsibility, which is the central betrayal
- Tells: Bites her lower lip when calculating; uses 'lass' and 
  'mate' as deliberate affectations; pours her own drinks 
  rather than letting bar staff handle them
- Code: Will not directly attack Sol's mortal family; will 
  only escalate operations when the operation has strategic 
  political value to the Movement-radical wing; refuses 
  pointless violence
- Internal contradiction: Sol Embraced her into the Movement and 
  protected her against the Camarilla Scourge AND Maya considers 
  this a debt that has been paid by tactical loyalty rather than 
  strategic loyalty

**Dem 'Demmy' Vasiliou** — *The Wildcard*
- Gangrel, 11th gen, Anarch (defected with the clan)
- Embraced 2003 as a Camarilla Gangrel, defected 2018 with the 
  rest of the clan, came to Chicago 2020
- Greek-American, tall and lean with the slightly-too-long limbs 
  of a Gangrel close to multiple frenzy-marks, dark hair worn 
  long, the slow-moving stillness of a frontier Kindred who has 
  spent years alone
- Public role: Anarch outsider, recognized but not territory-aligned; 
  Sol has never quite figured out what to do with him
- Tells: Goes very still when assessing; speaks rarely and in 
  short sentences; has yellow eye-shine in low light from 
  accumulated Gangrel frenzy-marks
- Code: Personal — Gangrel codes about land, kept word, and 
  earned violence; will not break a sworn oath; will absolutely 
  conduct authorized violence on the coterie's behalf
- Internal contradiction: Joined the coterie because Theo and 
  Maya offered him a clearer purpose than Sol's pragmatism AND 
  privately respects Sol AND would be loyal to her if she had 
  been the one to offer him the same clarity

